{
  "stem": "6878.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I brought him an electric kettle present that he should see-- see what he can do if he can get the job back.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But unfortunately, he didn't come back to us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He didn't-- he was afraid.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He says, I'm afraid to stick out my neck.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that was the end of the job from there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Motel?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we had to--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'll tell you.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My one brother-- my two brothers were in Africa, one in Rhodesia and one in Johannesburg, South Africa in Krugersdorp.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The other brother we left-- one brother we left in Russia.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He remained in Russia, which is a little story I'll tell you later.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my sisters were all in the shtetl.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My three sisters were in the shtetl.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And when they first-- what they did, the German-- the Lithuanian, actually, what they did is they collected the strongest men from the shtetl, the biggest men, the strongest one.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they took him near the church, which I-- after the war, I saw where the place was.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they shot him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There were about 12 of them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they were then dragged down near the river, and they were buried there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father was-- my father died in 1935.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When I was in the army, my father died.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He died of-- he was ill for a while, and he was died.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She started going to labor early in the morning.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when I was in the army, in the Lithuanian Army, I knew one professor, by the name Professor Zacharin.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was a gynecologist.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I went to him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I knew that he's in ghetto.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I knew where it is.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We already kept an eye on this.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
